## About This Project

This project is a Python-based tool developed to perform an audit of open-source software dependencies.

The OSS Insight Scanner analyzes packages used in a project, identifies their licenses, detects known vulnerabilities, and generates a structured audit report.

This project demonstrates key open-source concepts such as transparency, security, and compliance.

