## Features

* Reads project dependencies
* Identifies open-source licenses
* Detects known vulnerabilities
* Generates audit reports
* Provides summary analysis

---

## Module Description

### Dependency Reader

Reads dependency files (like requirements.txt) and extracts package details.

### License Checker

Matches packages with their respective open-source licenses.

### Vulnerability Checker

Checks for known security vulnerabilities in packages.

### Report Generator

Creates a structured report showing package name, version, license, and vulnerability status.

### Summary Analyzer

Displays total packages scanned, safe packages, and vulnerable packages.

